node.text:
Everyone, meet Cassie. She’s one hell of a bartenderoni, and we are straight #blessed to have her on our team. She’s been with us for almost 3 years now, and she is still as feisty as the day we met her. This Zodiac Scorpio, Ascendant Taurus with a Moon in Libra has some stories to tell and opinions to give, so settle in and listen up! 🗣👂🏻
•
When she’s not busy cleaning toilets and slingin’ beers at Angry Chair, she spends her free time trying to sell dream catchers and  spell books barefoot at local gas stations, going on “YAK ATTACKS”, charging her crystals on the night of a full moon, and slathering everything she eats with vegan mayonnaise. Angry Chair wouldn’t be the same without her. Cheers to you, Cassie! 🍻
•
#angrychairbrewing #stayangry #employeespotlight #ouremployeesmakeus #yakattack #werd #whatascorpio

node.text:
•
Everyone, meet Staci. She’s one of our fun-loving and friendly bartenders. She’s been with us for a whopping 3 months now, but she is a part of the Angry Chair family all the same. She might be a fresh face to some of you, so strap in and learn a thing or two about this rad newbie. 👶
•
When she’s not busy slingin’ beers at The Chair, she spends her time going on adventures with her dogs, riding out with her Jeep Crew, and chugging large amounts of Duke’s Mayonnaise in Wyoming while blaring new age country music. She’s got enough energy for the entire staff combined, and we can always count on her to walk through the door with a smile on her face. Cheers to you, Staci!🍻
•
#angrychairbrewing #stayangry #employeespotlight #ouremployeesmakeus #mush #werd

node.text:
•
Everyone, meet Scotty. He’s one of our righteously rowdy and rambunctious bartenders. He’s been with us since 2016 and we’ve loved every second of it. Take a look into what make him tick, and you might just learn something about him you never would’ve otherwise.
•
When he’s not busy slinging’ beers, he spends his time yelling at hurricanes, building massive 7800 piece LEGO projects, and playing a copious amount of video games while drinking Four Loko, most likely until the sun comes up. He has a massive heart and an even bigger personality, and while his music taste might be 🗑 he fits in perfectly with the rest of the AC fam. Cheers to you, Scotty! 🍻
•
#angrychairbrewing #stayangry #employeespotlight #ouremployeesmakeus #mush #werd

node.text:
🎉5️⃣ANNIVERSARY UPDATE5️⃣🎉
•
Our 5 year anniversary party is just TWO short weeks away! We are incredibly stoked to party with you all and humbled we’ve made it this far with your support.
•
In this video y’all will see a walk through of the check in process, where you will need to provide you and your plus one’s ID, get checked off of the list, and wrist-banded. From there you can make your way inside and start drinking. ALL BEERS WILL BE $5 EACH AND WILL VARY IN POUR SIZES DEPENDING ON THE SYLE. On your WAY OUT, you will be able to pick up your glassware as well as your bottle of Grand Cru.
•
Draft list, subject to change:

4th Anniversary Grand Cru
5th Anniversary Grand Cru
Barrel Aged German Chocolate Cupcake Stout
Barrel Aged Peanut Butter Marshmallow Popinski
Barrel Aged Russian Interference
Barrel Aged Dave’s Barleywine
Barrel Aged Ultra Violence
Chocolate Covered Cherry Imp. Stout
Peanut Butter Banana Bread
Peanut Butter and Jelly Imp. Stout
2 Nut Chump
Orange Puffs
Yellow Puffs
Raspberry Tart Berliner
Equilibrium Collab DIPA
Space Grass
...AND MORE TO COME. STAY TUNED.
•
PLEASE arrive approximately 30 minutes before your ticketed session begins. This will help us check everyone in in a quick and orderly fashion. As always, PLEASE UBER, LYFT, TELEPORT, CARPOOL, GET DROPPED OFF BY YOUR GRANDMA, OR HECK, RIDE A UNICYCLE HERE.
•
Our good friends @mouthole will be providing the tasty eats for the anniversary! Stay tuned for a detailed menu in the near future. WERDDDDD! 🤘
•
#angrychairbrewing #stayangry #angrychairturns5 #5yearanniversary #werd

🥊𝑹𝒀𝑬 𝑩𝑨𝑹𝑹𝑬𝑳 𝑨𝑮𝑬𝑫 𝑷𝑶𝑷𝑰𝑵𝑺𝑲𝑰 𝒘/ 𝑽𝑨𝑵𝑰𝑳𝑳𝑨🥊
•
Available in the tasting room starting today, this iteration of Popinski was aged in locally sourced Wild Buck Rye Whiskey barrels from NJOY Spirits Distillery in Weeki Wachi, FL for 15 months. Then, we decided to add a bunch of vanilla. And it came out deeeeeelish. 11.5% ABV. Does not contain lactose. $35 each. 
•
We have reserved a limited amount to be placed on OZNR this coming Sunday, August 22nd at 1PM EST. We WILL be allowing proxies. 🤝 The pickup window for OZNR orders will be from 08/23- 08/29 during operational hours. Thank you for your cooperation.

#angrychairbrewing #stayangry #popinski

📝𝙱𝙻𝙰𝙽𝙺 𝙿𝙰𝙶𝙴𝚂📝
•
Blank Pages is a new Oat Milk IPA that we double dry hopped with Galaxy, Idaho 007 and Citra. We made the oat milk in house and dosed it into the whirlpool, along with a hefty dose of Galaxy. The end result is a hop forward beer, with medium body and maximum drinkability. 7.2% ABV. Yes crowlerz✅
Open 3-10 today, come pick up your OZNR orders of Rye Barrel Aged Popinski and grab a beer! See y’all soon. 😎🤘
•
#angrychairbrewing #stayangry #werd

Freshly canned this morning, 𝓛𝓸𝓻𝓭 𝓑𝔂𝓻𝓸𝓷 makes its triumphant return! This Double IPA starts with a Pilsner base and a hefty dose of white wheat, then gets double dry-hopped with Nelson Sauvin + Strata. 8.8% ABV. Available in 4-packs and on draft now. Open 12-10PM today y’all. See ya sooooon! Werrrrrrd! 🤘

We have not one, but two bottles available starting today in the tasting room. Open from 12-10PM today, so come grab a some bottles and hang! 
•
☕️🍫🍦SLOTH LOVE COFFEE🍦🍫☕️ is our 10.5% ABV spin off of ROCKY ROAD, that sees the addition of hazelnut coffee that melds harmoniously with the walnuts, Dominican cacao and marshmallow. The result is a surprisingly sippable after dinner treat. 🥛Contains Lactose.
•
🍫🍦ROCKY ROAD🍦🍫 is our 10.5% ABV Imperial Sweet Stout treated with absurd amounts of freshly hand toasted walnuts, Dominican Cacao nibs, and ooey-gooey marshmallows. This beer drinks like melted Rocky Road ice cream and it’s one of our all time favorites. 🥛Contains Lactose.
•
We have reserved a limited amount to be placed on OZNR this coming Monday, August 2nd at 7PM EST. We WILL be allowing proxies. 🤝 The pickup window for OZNR orders will be from 08/03- 08/09 during operational hours. Thank you for your cooperation.
